{"tid":1041240,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[友情] 我咁樣算唔算做咗工具人？","createTime":"2019-02-28T16:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T04:34:26.000Z","uid":7559,"like":83,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"64957708a8f8e1d19b34fb67a201dfd73f5eadee","tid":1041240,"uid":7559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:35:23.000Z","msg":"是咁的 有啲長<br />\n<br />\n上個sem我有個frd讀同我讀同一個course <br />\n個course就出咗份功課 <br />\n份功課都幾難下 有10題要做<br />\n加上個lecturer都幾閪下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我就Deadline兩個禮拜前搵我個frd一齊做一齊傾啦 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[Deadline前兩個禮拜]<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 份功課好似有啲難喎 不如一齊早啲一齊做一齊傾？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔畀屎我咁算啦，唯有死死氣自己搞掂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我每晚通頂做 做足兩個禮拜 先做得完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[Deadline前一日]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 份功課搞唔掂，可唔可以send你份答案嚟see see?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: ✅✅ （我心諗我通咗2個禮拜頂，一句說話就想拎我答案？諗下好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 情況就好似有個Freerider，去到諗尾先諗住搶功勞咁）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁話晒識咗咁多年 又同一個Group <br />\n無理由就咁一份功課就斷咗段友誼<br />\n所以之後都有一齊上堂  傾計<br />\n咁到今個Sem 我又同佢Reg咗第二個Course<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個Course出咗份功課 <br />\n但係呢份功課冇之前個Course嗰份咁難<br />\n諗住做完同佢Check下答案啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[Now]<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：不如一齊Check下答案？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：其實你唔洗問我啦，當初我走頭無路嘅時候問你拎答案，你都冇理我。如果唔係有其他Friend救我，我嗰個Course肥咗喇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：起佢飛腳啦 佢根本淨係當你工具人 識咗咁多年都係咁話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：朋友緊係唔計較邊個付出得多啲 快啲道歉啦"},{"pid":"01f9d07acb89ab183d2ae3b88fce62502989b67d","tid":1041240,"uid":90323,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:45:11.000Z","msg":"30幾歲嘅呀叔話我知，<br />\n沒有永遠嘅朋友， 只有永遠嘅利益。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我睇法係， 簡朋友隨左有計傾外，要簡性格好， 如果唔係識左好耐被出賣會好失落。唔sure岩唔岩用係你呢個case"},{"pid":"accd759b97caf937caa5901bd31153e7a0756b52","tid":1041240,"uid":57255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:57:35.000Z","msg":"佢以為你想抄考佢份答案, 所以先reject你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00083d4d25bbd7d997d9c65a2750da685874aaf4","tid":1041240,"uid":239775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T17:15:11.000Z","msg":"擺明搵你笨, 見你醒目即刻扮受害者"},{"pid":"4fcc126899d8827cca36e71d0de590ef7bde0419","tid":1041240,"uid":7559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"accd759b97caf937caa5901bd31153e7a0756b52","tid":1041240,"uid":57255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:57:35.000Z","msg":"佢以為你想抄考佢份答案, 所以先reject你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T19:28:56.000Z","msg":"我係成份功課scan好咗 Send俾佢 之後問佢Check唔check answer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a63a7566c79ce745bac09432e145c6d6bd0ae0","tid":1041240,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T19:35:37.000Z","msg":"咁你咪拎返上次件事嚟講囉<br />\n雖然呢啲人都唔值得同佢繼續講嘢<br />\n除非你犯賤心軟要乞個所謂朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c4a7f787740a5188335fd0f56d98b7bf2b5ab36","tid":1041240,"uid":7559,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a2a63a7566c79ce745bac09432e145c6d6bd0ae0","tid":1041240,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T19:35:37.000Z","msg":"咁你咪拎返上次件事嚟講囉<br />\n雖然呢啲人都唔值得同佢繼續講嘢<br />\n除非你犯賤心軟要乞個所謂朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T19:36:51.000Z","msg":"唔知點開口好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢會唔會好憎我唔想理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d9a802fcd1f498e877633ca391db0c013fff44","tid":1041240,"uid":52271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T19:44:13.000Z","msg":"當初佢搵你求救，你冇理佢，我唔覺你係錯嘅<br />\n第二份功課你搵佢&quot;check&quot;答案，我站在佢角度，有兩個可能<br />\n1 你冇做想抄佢，我諗佢都係咁諗，所以佢咁回應你。呢個回應都正常嘅，既然你拒絕左佢求救，佢怨你都正常<br />\n2 你有做，真心想&quot;check&quot;，講真，呢想仲膠，你咁做一係屎忽痕，一係潤鳩佢。其實你拒絕佢，佢心中實有啲野，我唔知之後你地相處係扮冇野定已經疏遠左。總之係變左質<br />\n我冇judge你地對錯，但我睇單野就係咁"},{"pid":"a3713636f9a6866e6c98a0318444a793886a03c8","tid":1041240,"uid":85586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c4a7f787740a5188335fd0f56d98b7bf2b5ab36","tid":1041240,"uid":7559,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a2a63a7566c79ce745bac09432e145c6d6bd0ae0","tid":1041240,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T19:35:37.000Z","msg":"咁你咪拎返上次件事嚟講囉<br />\n雖然呢啲人都唔值得同佢繼續講嘢<br />\n除非你犯賤心軟要乞個所謂朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T19:36:51.000Z","msg":"唔知點開口好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢會唔會好憎我唔想理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T19:47:37.000Z","msg":"無眼睇<br />\n既然你覺得佢呢個朋友咁重要唔可以得罪嘅<br />\n咁你都係去乞求佢嘅原諒吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真呢個世界無話冇咗邊個唔得<br />\n我就覺得無乜需要受呢啲氣"},{"pid":"e50af4f0f422fea30e4e176661225f13d61a